sections.heading: to 31-18A-9 - Repealed.
sections.text: Repeals.— Laws 1994, ch. 19, § 4, repealed 31-18A-1 to 31-18A-9 NMSA 1978, as enacted by Laws 1988, ch. 116, §§ 1 to 9, the Sentencing Guidelines Act, effective July 1, 1994. For provisions of former sections,seethe 1993 NMSA 1978 onNMOneSource.com.
